{"tid":1287500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如7月6都玩下airdrop","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:30:33.000Z","uid":53349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f12ec67f8e482cbf9a41d5f37f01f52cc350737","tid":1287500,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人講過咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然當日主題不離光復屯門公園，咁齋行都悶，咪㩒下手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如真係藍黃齊上街，就不如順便分享下武漢既情況。難得約埋出黎行街，咪交流下，we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比佢地睇清楚，有朝一日為民生而上街反抗真係會比人鎮壓，唔係我地啲黃係道抹黑佢地既祖國。咁佢地當日出得黎就應該輕鬆代入到個角色(可能都要返啲引導既)，嘗試令佢地理解我地反政府係有必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情況再樂觀啲既甚至為77做到少少鋪路，人數上加持。不過我都冇咩期望佢地會加入77，同埋一時三刻都好難磨合到，佢地加入可能有副作用都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n概念大約係咁樣，唔識做呢類宣傳，略盡綿力，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f43c070e0d2bb9924ab7691c0de69c9e4ed36d","tid":1287500,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6b93823aade1ec6d3eb21623bce87a3bc523a97","tid":1287500,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95a410f3311ab4be2a0e5d3599cedee10f53b8e","tid":1287500,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}